            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 09-02-98 02:29 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I am trying to find out how many Chrome and Gold finish Star Wars PEZ were made for the 1997 ToyFair and what they are currently worth. Can anyone help? I have looked everywhere.</font>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Thanks<br>
